IMAPAccount unm
Host outlook.office365.com
User jabelcastellanosjoo@unm.edu
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
PassCmd "~/.local/scripts/mail_scripts/mutt_oauth2.py ~/.local/scripts/mail_scripts/jabelcastellanosjoo@unm.edu.tokens"
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile ~/.maildir/certificates/root-certificates.pem

IMAPStore unm-remote
Account unm

MaildirStore unm-local
Path ~/Mail/unm/
Inbox ~/Mail/unm/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel unm
Far :unm-remote:
Near :unm-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

